Information

Sex Diaries: Trans Lovers
Charlie Russell meets men who describe themselves as heterosexual and are looking for love with transgender women who still have male genitalia. Harlen is in the process of leaving his heterosexual wife of 10 years for singer Geri, while single guy Andy is looking to lose his trans-virginity, and 51-year-old window cleaner Mark has been a regular on the scene for five years. The programme also views this complex dating process through the eyes of transgender women, including 42-year-old Paige.
